intent: Which are the car makers which produce at least 2 models and more than 3 car makers ? snippet: select t1.id ,  t1.maker from car_makers as t1 join model_list as t2 on t1.id  =  t2.maker group by t1.id having count(*)  >=  2 intersect select t1.id ,  t1.maker from car_makers as t1 join model_list as t2 on t1.id  =  t2.maker join car_names as t3 on t2.model  =  t3.model group by t1.id having count(*)  >  3;

snippet: SELECT T1.Id ,  T1.Maker FROM CAR_MAKERS AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.Maker GROUP BY T1.Id HAVING count(*)  >=  2 INTERSECT SELECT T1.Id ,  T1.Maker FROM CAR_MAKERS AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Id  =  T2.Maker JOIN CAR_NAMES AS T3 ON T2.model  =  T3.model GROUP BY T1.Id HAVING count(*)  >  3;

snippet: SELECT T1.countryId ,  T1.CountryName FROM Countries AS T1 JOIN CAR_MAKERS AS T2 ON T1.CountryId  =  T2.Country GROUP BY T1.countryId HAVING count(*)  >  3 UNION SELECT T1.countryId ,  T1.CountryName FROM Countries AS T1 JOIN CAR_MAKERS AS T2 ON T1.CountryId  =  T2.Country JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T3 ON T2.Id  =  T3.Maker WHERE T3.Model  =  'fiat';

intent: What are the ids and names of all countries that either have more than 3 car makers or produce fiat model ? | car_1 | continents : ContId ( Kyle ), Continent | countries : CountryId ( Kyle ), CountryName, Continent | car_makers : Id ( Kyle ), Maker, FullName, Country | model_list : ModelId ( Kyle ), Maker, Model | car_names : MakeId ( Kyle ), Model, Make | cars_data : Id ( Kyle ), MPG, Cylinders, Edispl, Horsepower, Weight, Accelerate, Year
snippet: select t1.countryid ,  t1.countryname from countries as t1 join car_makers as t2 on t1.countryid  =  t2.country group by t1.countryid having count(*)  >  3 union select t1.countryid ,  t1.countryname from countries as t1 join car_makers as t2 on t1.countryid  =  t2.country join model_list as t3 on t2.id  =  t3.maker where t3.model  =  'fiat';

intent: Show the names of singers and the total sales of their songs. | singer | singer : Singer_ID ( Kyle ), Name, Birth_Year, Net_Worth_Millions, Citizenship | song : Song_ID ( Kyle ), Title, Singer_ID, Sales, Highest_Position
snippet: SELECT T1.Name ,  sum(T2.Sales) FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID GROUP BY T1.Name

intent: For each singer name, what is the total sales for their songs? | singer | singer : Singer_ID ( Kyle ), Name, Birth_Year, Net_Worth_Millions, Citizenship | song : Song_ID ( Kyle ), Title, Singer_ID, Sales, Highest_Position
snippet: SELECT T1.Name ,  sum(T2.Sales) FROM singer AS T1 JOIN song AS T2 ON T1.Singer_ID  =  T2.Singer_ID GROUP BY T1.Name

intent: List the name of singers that do not have any song. | singer | singer : Singer_ID ( Kyle ), Name, Birth_Year, Net_Worth_Millions, Citizenship | song : Song_ID ( Kyle ), Title, Singer_ID, Sales, Highest_Position
snippet: SELECT Name FROM singer WHERE Singer_ID NOT IN (SELECT Singer_ID FROM song)

intent: What is the sname of every sing that does not have any song? | singer | singer : Singer_ID ( Kyle ), Name, Birth_Year, Net_Worth_Millions, Citizenship | song : Song_ID ( Kyle ), Title, Singer_ID, Sales, Highest_Position
snippet: SELECT Name FROM singer WHERE Singer_ID NOT IN (SELECT Singer_ID FROM song)

intent: Show the citizenship shared by singers with birth year before 1945 and after 1955. | singer | singer : Singer_ID ( Kyle ), Name, Birth_Year, Net_Worth_Millions, Citizenship | song : Song_ID ( Kyle ), Title, Singer_ID, Sales, Highest_Position
snippet: SELECT Citizenship FROM singer WHERE Birth_Year  <  1945 INTERSECT SELECT Citizenship FROM singer WHERE Birth_Year  >  1955

intent: What are the citizenships that are shared by singers with a birth year before 1945 and after 1955? | singer | singer : Singer_ID ( Kyle ), Name, Birth_Year, Net_Worth_Millions, Citizenship | song : Song_ID ( Kyle ), Title, Singer_ID, Sales, Highest_Position
snippet: SELECT Citizenship FROM singer WHERE Birth_Year  <  1945 INTERSECT SELECT Citizenship FROM singer WHERE Birth_Year  >  1955

intent: How many available features are there in total? | real_estate_properties | Ref_Feature_Types : feature_type_code ( Kyle ), feature_type_name | Ref_Property_Types : property_type_code ( Kyle ), property_type_description | Other_Available_Features : feature_id ( Kyle ), feature_type_code, feature_name, feature_description | Properties : property_id ( Kyle ), property_type_code, date_on_market, date_sold, property_name, property_address, room_count, vendor_requested_price, buyer_offered_price, agreed_selling_price, apt_feature_1, apt_feature_2, apt_feature_3, fld_feature_1, fld_feature_2, fld_feature_3, hse_feature_1, hse_feature_2, hse_feature_3, oth_feature_1, oth_feature_2, oth_feature_3, shp_feature_1, shp_feature_2, shp_feature_3, other_property_details | Other_Property_Features : property_id, feature_id, property_feature_description
snippet: SELECT count(*) FROM Other_Available_Features

intent: What is the feature type name of feature AirCon? | real_estate_properties | Ref_Feature_Types : feature_type_code ( Kyle ), feature_type_name | Ref_Property_Types : property_type_code ( Kyle ), property_type_description | Other_Available_Features : feature_id ( Kyle ), feature_type_code, feature_name, feature_description | Properties : property_id ( Kyle ), property_type_code, date_on_market, date_sold, property_name, property_address, room_count, vendor_requested_price, buyer_offered_price, agreed_selling_price, apt_feature_1, apt_feature_2, apt_feature_3, fld_feature_1, fld_feature_2, fld_feature_3, hse_feature_1, hse_feature_2, hse_feature_3, oth_feature_1, oth_feature_2, oth_feature_3, shp_feature_1, shp_feature_2, shp_feature_3, other_property_details | Other_Property_Features : property_id, feature_id, property_feature_description
snippet: SELECT T2.feature_type_name FROM Other_Available_Features AS T1 JOIN Ref_Feature_Types AS T2 ON T1.feature_type_code  =  T2.feature_type_code WHERE T1.feature_name  =  "AirCon"

intent: Show the property type descriptions of properties belonging to that code. | real_estate_properties | Ref_Feature_Types : feature_type_code ( Kyle ), feature_type_name | Ref_Property_Types : property_type_code ( Kyle ), property_type_description | Other_Available_Features : feature_id ( Kyle ), feature_type_code, feature_name, feature_description | Properties : property_id ( Kyle ), property_type_code, date_on_market, date_sold, property_name, property_address, room_count, vendor_requested_price, buyer_offered_price, agreed_selling_price, apt_feature_1, apt_feature_2, apt_feature_3, fld_feature_1, fld_feature_2, fld_feature_3, hse_feature_1, hse_feature_2, hse_feature_3, oth_feature_1, oth_feature_2, oth_feature_3, shp_feature_1, shp_feature_2, shp_feature_3, other_property_details | Other_Property_Features : property_id, feature_id, property_feature_description
snippet: SELECT T2.property_type_description FROM Properties AS T1 JOIN Ref_Property_Types AS T2 ON T1.property_type_code  =  T2.property_type_code GROUP BY T1.property_type_code

intent: What are the names of properties that are either houses or apartments with more than 1 room? | real_estate_properties | Ref_Feature_Types : feature_type_code ( Kyle ), feature_type_name | Ref_Property_Types : property_type_code ( Kyle ), property_type_description | Other_Available_Features : feature_id ( Kyle ), feature_type_code, feature_name, feature_description | Properties : property_id ( Kyle ), property_type_code, date_on_market, date_sold, property_name, property_address, room_count, vendor_requested_price, buyer_offered_price, agreed_selling_price, apt_feature_1, apt_feature_2, apt_feature_3, fld_feature_1, fld_feature_2, fld_feature_3, hse_feature_1, hse_feature_2, hse_feature_3, oth_feature_1, oth_feature_2, oth_feature_3, shp_feature_1, shp_feature_2, shp_feature_3, other_property_details | Other_Property_Features : property_id, feature_id, property_feature_description
snippet: SELECT property_name FROM Properties WHERE property_type_code  =  "House" UNION SELECT property_name FROM Properties WHERE property_type_code  =  "Apartment" AND room_count  >  1
